greetingMessage: Welcome to the First Interview experience.
By answering just 5 free text questions, we can identify your candidate's personality traits and behaviours. Yes, really!
We'll then recommend candidates who match your success profile.
Everything you see here can be customised - text, colours, branding. Time to get creative!
We can even add videos to showcase you as an employer or give a taste of the job on offer.
If you want to know more about how this chat works click here.

If you’re good to go, fill in your details and press the Accept button. Use of our platform is subject to our Terms of Service and please check out our Privacy FAQs before you get started (if you are under 18, you may want to read these with a parent or guardian)
Before we get started, can I get your first name and last name?
title: Sapia.ai - Interview
missedDeadLineOrPersonalCommitment: Describe a time when you missed a deadline or personal commitment. How did that make you feel?
thingsDifferentlyQuestion: We are always hungry to learn and do things differently. Give an example of a time you have had to deal with change, professionally or personally?
ThanksMsg: Thanks for sharing that with us,
helpOutToTeam: 4. We believe that we are better together. Tell us about a time when you have rolled up your sleeves to help out your team or someone else?
difficultSituation: Have you ever dealt with someone difficult? How did you handle the situation? You can draw on your experiences at work, at school or any group activity
nationalIdentity: Do you identify as Aboriginal or Torres Strait Islander?
lookOutInboxProfileInformation: Great! That’s all the questions we have. Click the button below to submit your responses, and keep an eye out in your inbox for your personality profile.
